data.title: Pubs To Watch West Ham
data.meta_description: Need a pub to watch West Ham football matches? Use FANZO to find you a local option that's guaranteed to show the match in just a few seconds.
data.text:
On this page you’ll find a list of all the best pubs showing West Ham matches near you. If that’s what your here for, perfect. Scroll down to the Hammer’s fixtures below, click the one you’d like to see and hit the yellow ‘Find Venues’ button. After you type in your location we’ll bring up a list of every sports bar and pub showing the game nearby. Prefer a more general look at the best venues around the UK showing sport? Well then our guide to the best pubs showing Premier League is the one for you.

Need a guiding hand to push you towards pubs showing West Ham games? This page was tailor made for people just like you. Our handy pub tool below eliminates all the pain in finding the perfect venue to watch a match. After you’ve picked a fixture you want to watch, select it from the list below and select the ‘Find Venues’ button. From there you just need to enter your location or an area in which you’d like to watch the game and we’ll do the rest. West Ham fans were hit with a mixture of excitement and trepidation when moving from storied Upton Park to the more modern Olympic Stadium. They were also surprised to find a running track around the pitch, but no matter, the hallmark of a big club, a 21st century stadium was theirs. A few tumultuous years and a couple of flirts with relegation later, they seem to have found their feet. Huge wins over all the top clubs, a couple of European tours and cost-efficient signings have pushed the Hammers back towards the glory days. With captain, leader, legend Mark Noble retired though who will be the next man to write himself into their history books. One things for sure, if you endear yourselves to the West Ham faithful they will never, ever forget you. If you can’t wait for the next Hammer’s match why not check our Premier League TV guide? All the upcoming fixtures are there for you to browse through.
